@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Frequently Asked Questions";
}

<header>
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="~/css/faq.css">
</header>

<body>
    <section>
        <h2>1. What is the purpose of this website?</h2>
        <p>This website provides users with detailed information about football teams, including match details, player statistics, and much more.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>2. How do I subscribe to the newsletter?</h2>
        <p>To subscribe, simply enter your email address in the subscription form located at the bottom of the homepage.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>3. How can I update my personal data?</h2>
        <p>You can update your personal information by visiting your account settings and modifying the relevant details.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>4. How can I delete my account?</h2>
        <p>If you would like to delete your account, please contact our support team via the contact form or email.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>5. Is my personal information safe?</h2>
        <p>Yes, we take your privacy seriously. Your personal data is securely stored with encrypted passwords and is accessible only by authorized personnel.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>6. How do I contact support?</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns, you can contact our support team at <a href="mailto:TopSCORERsupport@mail.com">TopSCORERsupport@mail.com</a>.</p>
    </section>

</body>
